sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as AgentConsole_UI
    participant NgRx as notifications_store
    participant SG as StatusGateway
    participant Svc as AgentConsoleStatusService

    UI->>NgRx: connectNotificationsSocket
    NgRx->>SG: connect (auth)
    SG->>Svc: buildSnapshot(user)
    Svc-->>SG: statusSnapshot
    SG-->>NgRx: statusSnapshot
    NgRx-->>UI: badges (spaces/workspaces/envs)

    Note over SG,NgRx: statusPatch on chat/automation/git change
    SG-->>NgRx: statusPatch
    NgRx-->>UI: play sound if not active env

    UI->>NgRx: markEnvironmentRead / setActiveEnvironment
    NgRx->>SG: emit to server
